<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Terms of Service</title>
    <style>
      @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap");
      :root {
        --bg-color: #111116;
        --card-bg-color: #191921;
        --border-color: #2a2a36;
        --primary-purple: #8a63d2;
        --text-light: #e0e0e0;
        --text-medium: #a0a0b0;
      }
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body { font-family: "Inter", system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background: var(--bg-color); color: var(--text-light); line-height: 1.6; }
      .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
      header { padding: 24px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
      header .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
      header a { color: var(--text-light); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
      h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); margin: 24px 0 12px; }
      h2 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin: 28px 0 10px; }
      p { color: var(--text-medium); margin: 8px 0; }
      ul { margin: 8px 0 8px 20px; color: var(--text-medium); }
      li { margin: 6px 0; }
      .card { background: var(--card-bg-color); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin: 16px 0; }
      footer { margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-medium); font-size: 0.95rem; }
      .pill { display: inline-block; padding: 6px 10px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 999px; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-medium); }
      .accent { color: var(--primary-purple); font-weight: 600; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <div class="brand">
          <a href="/">← Back</a>
          <span class="pill">Terms of Service</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main>
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="accent">Last updated: <%= new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10) %></p>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>Acceptance</h2>
          <p>By inviting or using the bot, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>Use of the Bot</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>You must comply with Discord's Terms of Service and Community Guidelines.</li>
            <li>You will not misuse the bot to harass, spam, or otherwise disrupt servers.</li>
            <li>The bot is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>Data</h2>
          <p>The bot stores limited configuration data necessary for functionality, as described in the <a href="/privacy" style="color:inherit; text-decoration: underline;">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>Service Availability</h2>
          <p>We may modify, suspend, or discontinue the bot or any part of it at any time <strong>without prior notice</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, we are not liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the bot.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>For questions about these Terms, contact the bot owner via the support server or listed contact method.</p>
        </div>
      </main>

      <footer>
        <p>
          © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Garden Tracker • <a href="/privacy" style="color:inherit">Privacy</a> • <a href="/tos" style="color:inherit">Terms</a>
        </p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
  </html>


